The '''Galactic Chirgotta Awareness Council''' was formed to heighten the public awareness of the intestinal [[Parasite/Legends|parasite]] [[Chirgotta]] and to encourage good intestinal hygiene. It frequently held public events with entertainer performances to inform the public about the parasite.

{{Stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The council is mentioned in the mission "Chirgotta Awareness Council Grant" which is available at Entertainer Mission Terminals in ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]''. A booking agent hires the player to perform at a certain location to promote the council's goals.

